scripts.gitTag: git add . ; git commit -m "$npm_package_name-v$npm_package_version"; git tag $npm_package_name-v$npm_package_version
scripts.version:patch: npm version patch --no-git-tag-version;git st; npm run gitTag
scripts.version:minor: npm version minor --no-git-tag-version;git st; npm run gitTag
scripts.version:major: npm version major --no-git-tag-version;git st; npm run gitTag
